Sparks shot through the alley as Swithchblades wrist blades collided with
the sword. The echo of metal and crackling energy filled the air.
Switchblade turned sideways so he was even with Grimlock. his right arm was
positioned to his side as a defensive maneuver, his left blade was drawn
back much like a scorpions tale waiting for an opening to strike. The Cybrat
leader feighned a quick jab toward the Dinobots chest and quickly followed
with an uppercut toward the mechanical crotch area attempting to slice
Grimlock in half.

Machine gun shots from Jet Lee (Close enough) filled the air causing a
series of dents to form from Switchblades left leg up to his thigh. The
impact hadn't penetrated his shell yet but Switchblade knew that if he took
his concentration off of his airborn opponent he'd be cut into so many
little pieces that all the kings horses and all the kings men couldn't put
him together again.
